that we should just kill ourselves, hmm?

12
00:00:46,004 --> 00:00:47,088
And besides,

13
00:00:47,589 --> 00:00:50,467
knowing those assholes
are gonna die, too, is nice.

14
00:00:50,967 --> 00:00:52,469
They make me sick.

15
00:00:54,429 --> 00:00:55,930
Why don't we just do it?

16
00:00:56,765 --> 00:00:58,641
